posting_body: ['Yarrowood Highlands', '11330 NE 36th Place, Bellevue, WA, 98004', 'Use this link for more info:', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 61', 'OR Text', '61', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text with us.', 'Bellevue Apartment Living.', 'Your Style.', 'Welcome to Yarrowood Highlands', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1208 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Here at the Yarrowood Highlands we feature sophisticated and spacious two and three bedroom floor plans within our connected Bellevue community.', 'Our homes are in a serene neighborhood, surrounded by lush green spaces and located near the Kirkland Waterfront, with a conducive amount of walking space and pet relief area.', 'Whether you are ready to relax or recharge, an abundance of amenities and activities can be found right outside your front door.', 'Unwind on your personal patio or balcony, take a bike ride through nearby Watershed Park or take a dip in our resort-style pool and spa.', 'Choose style seamlessly blended with luxury, and make your move to Yarrowood Highlands today.', 'Features', '- Marble Entry Foyers*', '- Personal Patios and Balconies*', '- Two- and Three-Bedroom Residences', '- Air Conditioning', '- Open-Concept Living Areas', '- Granite Countertops Throughout', '- Wood-Style Flooring in Kitchens*', '- Cozy, In-Suite Fireplace*', '- Maple-Wood Cabinetry', '*in select units', 'Community Amenities', '- Fifteen minutes to downtown Seattle', '- Resort-Inspired Pool', '- Ten minutes to downtown Redmond', '- Marble Entry Foyers*', '- Relaxing Spa', '- Professional On-Site Management', '- Twenty minutes to downtown Seattle', '- Community Playground', '- Five minutes to downtown Kirkland', '- Online Rent Payments and Service Requests', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Saturday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Pet Policy', 'Pets - allowed', 'Bellevue Apartments Redmond Seattle Kirkland', '7CzX1dtRGa']
